@{
    Layout = null;
}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Error 500 - Error interno</title>
    <style>
        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        body {
            min-height: 100vh;
            font-family: "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
            display: grid;
            place-items: center;
            padding: 24px;
            background:
                radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(255,153,102,.16), transparent 28%),
                radial-gradient(circle at bottom right, rgba(15,68,137,.18), transparent 30%),
                linear-gradient(135deg, #fff5ef 0%, #eef5ff 45%, #f7fbff 100%);
            color: #18366f;
        }
        .card {
            width: min(760px, 100%);
            background: rgba(255,255,255,.9);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.72);
            border-radius: 32px;
            padding: 42px 32px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 24px 60px rgba(24,54,111,.12);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        }
        .brand {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 18px;
            color: #234f92;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .brand-badge {
            width: 42px;
            height: 42px;
            border-radius: 14px;
            display: grid;
            place-items: center;
            color: white;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f4489, #56a8ff);
        }
        .code {
            font-size: clamp(84px, 20vw, 150px);
            line-height: .95;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: #d05b2d;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 42px);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        p {
            color: #4e648d;
            font-size: 17px;
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        .actions {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 14px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .btn {
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 18px;
            padding: 14px 22px;
            font-weight: 700;
            transition: .25s ease;
        }
        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f4489, #225d93);
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 14px 28px rgba(34,93,147,.28);
        }
        .btn-secondary {
            background: #fff1e8;
            color: #9a4a26;
            border: 1px solid #ffd7c2;
        }
        .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <main class="card">
        <div class="brand">
            <span class="brand-badge">P</span>
            <span>ParkYa</span>
        </div>
        <div class="code">500</div>
        <h1>Ocurrio un problema interno</h1>
        <p>No pudimos completar la solicitud en este momento. Puedes volver al inicio o intentar nuevamente en unos minutos.</p>
        <div class="actions">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="@Url.Action("Index", "Home")">Ir al inicio</a>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="javascript:location.reload()">Intentar de nuevo</a>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
